$ Oracle: Init parameter STREAMS_POOL_SIZE
@ streams_pool_size

? The value of `streams_pool_size` controls the size of memory from the → development/databases/Oracle/architecture/instance/SGA that is made available for *Advanced Queueing*.

sa:

  → development/databases/Oracle/adminstration/init-parameters, `→ development/databases/Oracle/adminstration/init-parameters/sga/target`

  The hidden parameters
